            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="section-why-work-for-us">
        <div class="container section why-work-for-us">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h1>WHY WORK <span class="brand-color">FOR US</span></h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 transnational-company wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="brand-color">WE ARE A TRANSNATIONAL COMPANY THAT THINKS LIKE AN ENTREPRENEUR.</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">Our growth has resulted from a lean organization and flexible business model. We reward people who show initiative and creativity, and who demonstrate the energy to continually drive business forward. Despite our presence in different countries, we are agile enough to make quick decisions and act on opportunities when they arise.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 learning-development wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="brand-color">LEARNING & DEVELOPMENT</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">The knowledge we hold across our company, in our platforms, industrial assets and regions, is highly respected industry-wide. Our experts manage risks that can impact a product from source of origin to destination. Joining our business means becoming part of a team that skillfully coordinates every activity to make sure products get to where they are needed most.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-accolades-citations">
        <div class="container section accolades-citations">
            <div class="vector-image">
                <img src="~/Assets/Clients/images/why-work-for-us.png" alt="Why work for us">
            </div>
            <div class="container">
