                        <h4 class="year">2011</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">Global Trader Programme (GTP) Certificate</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-4 ribbon ribbon-2 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="year">2014</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">Global Trader Programme (GTP) Certificate</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-4 ribbon ribbon-3 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="year">2015</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">HRD Employer of Choice <span>Singapore Bronze winner in the &lt; 100 employees category</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-4 ribbon ribbon-1 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="year">2016</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">HRD Employer of Choice <span>- Work Culture</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-4 ribbon ribbon-2 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="year">2016</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">HRD Employer of Choice <span>- Access to Technology</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-4 ribbon ribbon-3 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h4 class="year">2018</h4>
                        <p class="font-20">Emerging 2018 - Singapore 1000 Award</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-professional-openings">
        <div id="careers" class="container section professional-openings">
            <form class="professional-openings" id="professional-openings" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="#">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                            <h2>PROFESSIONAL<br> <span class="brand-color">OPENINGS</span></h2>
                        </div>
                        <select name="position" id="company-position" class="wow fadeInUp company-position">
                            <option value="MANAGER, INTERNATIONAL MARKETING">MANAGER, INTERNATIONAL MARKETING</option>
                            <option value="DEPARTMENT HEAD">DEPARTMENT HEAD</option>
                            <option value="MARKETING">MARKETING</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                            <input type="text" name="name" class="name textfield" value="" placeholder="NAME" class="textfield" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                            <input type="text" name="experience" class="experience textfield" value="" placeholder="EXPERIENCE/QUALIFICATION" class="textfield" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 wow fadeInUp">
                            <input type="email" name="email" class="email textfield" value="" placeholder="EMAIL" class="textfield" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 wow fadeInUp">
                            <input type="file" name="uploadCV" class="uploadCV textfield" id="uploadCV" class="textfield" placeholder="UPLOAD CV" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                            <textarea class="textfield" name="message" class="message textfield" placeholder="MESSAGE" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                            <div class="button-container">
                                <input type="button" name="apply" value="APPLY" class="button-border professional-openings-send">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="msgapply" class="col-12 h3 text-center"></div>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="opportunities" class="section opportunities">
        <div class="opportunities-header">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 wow fadeInUp">
                        <h2>OPPORTUNITIES</h2>
                        <span class="suppliers-customers">SUPPLIERS &amp; CUSTOMERS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>.
        </div>
        <div class="container details wow fadeInUp">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                    <p class="font-20">We believe in nurturing a strong vendor base with organizations having the experience, knowledge and expertise in developing superior quality products. Our strategic vendor selection allows us to source and offer the best assortment of products, assuring finest quality supply at a very reasonable price.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                    <p class="font-20">Further, we aim to build a strong grid of reputed suppliers and foster an enduring partnership with them to serve clients better and stay ahead of the curve. We therefore welcome all suppliers to be a part of our extended family, and help us cater to needs of clients with the best possible solution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container opportunities-form wow fadeInUp">
            <div class="row">
                <form id="form-suppliers-customers" method="post" action="#" style="width: 100%">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="company-name" name="company-name" value="" placeholder="COMPANY NAME" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="contact-name" value="" placeholder="CONTACT NAME" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-details" name="contact-details" value="" placeholder="CONTACT DETAIL" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-city-country" name="contact-city-country" value="" placeholder="CITY &amp; COUNTRY" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-expertise" name="contact-expertise" value="" placeholder="AREA OF EXPERTISE" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-references" name="contact-references" value="" placeholder="REFERENCES / CLIENTELE" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="text" id="contact-business-together" name="contact-business-together" value="" placeholder="HOW CAN WE DO BUSINESS TOGETHER?" class="textfield" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="button-container">
                            <input type="button" name="submit" value="SUBMIT" class="button-border opportunities-send">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="msgSubmit" class="col-12 h3 text-center"></div>
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
